OL,3,CTop Gear: Chris Harris 'warned BBC of
OL,4,Csafety concerns' before Flintoff crash
OL,6,FSpeaking for the first time about what
OL,7,Fhappened, Harris said he feared
OL,8,FFlintoff had been killed, as ITV News'
OL,9,FAmy Lewis reports
OL,11,FFormer Top Gear presenter Chris Harris
OL,12,Fhas claimed he warned the BBC of
OL,13,Fsafety concerns before Andrew
OL,14,F"Freddie" Flintoff's injury on the
OL,15,Fshow in 2022.
