OL,3,CTop Gear: Chris Harris 'warned BBC of
OL,4,Csafety concerns' before Flintoff crash
OL,6,FFormer England cricketer Flintoff was
OL,7,Fbadly hurt in an accident during
OL,8,Ffilming at Dunsfold Aerodrome in
OL,9,FDecember 2022, leading to the BBC
OL,10,Fpausing the show "for the foreseeable
OL,11,Ffuture".
OL,13,FSpeaking about the accident on the Joe
OL,14,FRogan podcast, Harris said: "I ran to
OL,15,Fthe window, looked out, and he wasn't
OL,16,Fmoving.
OL,18,F"So I thought he was dead. I assumed
OL,19,Fhe was, then he moved."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
