OL,3,CTop Gear: Chris Harris 'warned BBC of
OL,4,Csafety concerns' before Flintoff crash
OL,6,FHarris added: "Three months before the
OL,7,Faccident, I'd gone to the BBC and
OL,8,Fsaid, 'Unless you change something,
OL,9,Fsomeone's going to die on this show'.
OL,11,F"So I went to them, I went to the BBC,
OL,12,Fand I told them my concerns from what
OL,13,FI'd seen as the most experienced
OL,14,Fdriver on the show by a mile.
OL,16,F"I said, 'If we carry on, at the very
OL,17,Fleast, we're going to have a serious
OL,18,Finjury, the very worst we have a
OL,19,Ffatality.'"
