OL,3,CTop Gear: Chris Harris 'warned BBC of
OL,4,Csafety concerns' before Flintoff crash
OL,6,FHarris also claimed he had asked to
OL,7,Fhave a meeting with the show's head of
OL,8,Fhealth and safety.
OL,10,FHe said: "What really killed me is
OL,11,Fthat no one's ever really acknowledged
OL,12,Fthe fact that I called it beforehand."
OL,14,FHarris continued: "I thought I'd done
OL,15,Fthe right thing. I'm not very good at
OL,16,Fthat. I normally just go with the flow
OL,17,Fbut I saw this coming.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
