OL,3,CTop Gear: Chris Harris 'warned BBC of
OL,4,Csafety concerns' before Flintoff crash
OL,6,F"I thought I did the right thing. I
OL,7,Fwent to the BBC and I found out really
OL,8,Fthat no one had taken me very
OL,9,Fseriously."
OL,11,FThe BBC said it will not comment on
OL,12,FChris Harris' comments, but instead
OL,13,Fissued a statement from BBC Studios on
OL,14,Fthe Health and Safety Review of Top
OL,15,FGear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
