OL,3,CTop Gear: Chris Harris 'warned BBC of
OL,4,Csafety concerns' before Flintoff crash
OL,6,F"The independent Health and production
OL,7,Freview of Top Gear, which looked at
OL,8,Fprevious seasons, found that while BBC
OL,9,FStudios had complied with the required
OL,10,FBBC policies and industry best
OL,11,Fpractice in making the show, there
OL,12,Fwere important learnings which would
OL,13,Fneed to be rigorously applied to
OL,14,Ffuture Top Gear UK productions," the
OL,15,Fstatement read.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
