OL,3,CTop Gear: Chris Harris 'warned BBC of
OL,4,Csafety concerns' before Flintoff crash
OL,6,F"The report included a number of
OL,7,Frecommendations to improve approaches
OL,8,Fto safety as Top Gear is a complex
OL,9,Fprogramme-making environment routinely
OL,10,Fnavigating tight filming schedules and
OL,11,Fambitious editorial expectations-
OL,12,Fchallenges often experienced by long-
OL,13,Frunning shows with an established on
OL,14,Fand off-screen team.
OL,16,F"Learnings included a detailed action
OL,17,Fplan involving changes in the way of
OL,18,Fworking, such as increased clarity on
OL,19,Froles and responsibilities and better
OL,20,Fcommunication between teams for any
OL,21,Ffuture Top Gear production."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
